incl (nat_sort l) l /\ incl l (nat_sort l)

nat_sort = fold_right nat_list_insert nil : list nat -> list nat Arguments nat_sort _%list_scope

nat_sort_length : forall l : list nat, length (nat_sort l) <= length l

incl_cons_inv : forall (A : Type) (a : A) (l m : list A), incl (a :: l) m -> In a m /\ incl l m
incl_cons : forall (A : Type) (a : A) (l m : list A), In a m -> incl l m -> incl (a :: l) m

ListDec.uniquify : forall A : Type, ListDec.decidable_eq A -> forall l : list A, exists l' : list A, NoDup l' /\ incl l l'
incl_app_inv : forall (A : Type) (l1 l2 m : list A), incl (l1 ++ l2) m -> incl l1 m /\ incl l2 m
ListDec.uniquify_map : forall A B : Type, ListDec.decidable_eq B -> forall (f : A -> B) (l : list A), exists l' : list A, NoDup (map f l') /\ incl (map f l) (map f l')
incl_tran : forall (A : Type) (l m n : list A), incl l m -> incl m n -> incl l n
list_an_app_inv : forall (a n : nat) (l r : list nat), list_an a n = l ++ r -> l = list_an a (length l) /\ r = list_an (a + length l) (length r)
incl_appr : forall (A : Type) (l m n : list A), incl l n -> incl l (m ++ n)
incl_appl : forall (A : Type) (l m n : list A), incl l n -> incl l (n ++ m)
NoDup_length_incl : forall (A : Type) (l l' : list A), NoDup l -> length l' <= length l -> incl l l' -> incl l' l
incl_app : forall (A : Type) (l m n : list A), incl l n -> incl m n -> incl (l ++ m) n
incl_tl : forall (A : Type) (a : A) (l m : list A), incl l m -> incl l (a :: m)
incl_refl : forall (A : Type) (l : list A), incl l l
nat_new_spec : forall l : list nat, ~ In (nat_new l) l
incl_nil_l : forall (A : Type) (l : list A), incl nil l
incl_l_nil : forall (A : Type) (l : list A), incl l nil -> l = nil
filter_In : forall (A : Type) (f : A -> bool) (x : A) (l : list A), In x (filter f l) < -> In x l /\ f x = One
NoDup_incl_length : forall (A : Type) (l l' : list A), NoDup l -> incl l l' -> length l <= length l'
Permutation.NoDup_Permutation_bis : forall (A : Type) (l l' : list A), NoDup l -> length l' <= length l -> incl l l' -> l ~p l'
in_map_iff : forall (A B : Type) (f : A -> B) (l : list A) (y : B), In y (map f l) < -> (exists x : A, f x = y /\ In x l)
NoDup_incl_NoDup : forall (A : Type) (l l' : list A), NoDup l -> length l' <= length l -> incl l l' -> NoDup l'
incl_app_app : forall (A : Type) (l1 l2 m1 m2 : list A), incl l1 m1 -> incl l2 m2 -> incl (l1 ++ l2) (m1 ++ m2)
incl_Forall_in_iff : forall (A : Type) (l l' : list A), incl l l' < -> Forall (fun x : A => In x l') l
nat_new = fun l : list nat => S (lmax l) : list nat -> nat Arguments nat_new _%list_scope
nat_list_insert_sorted : forall (x : nat) (l : list nat), nat_sorted l -> nat_sorted (nat_list_insert x l)
in_remove : forall (A : Type) (eq_dec : forall x y : A, {x = y} + {x <> y}) (l : list A) (x y : A), In x (remove eq_dec y l) -> In x l /\ x <> y
